articles.author: Matt Kew
articles.title: Wolff concedes Wikipedia comments about Verstappen "not the most intelligent" - Motorsport.com
articles.description: Toto Wolff concedes that playing down Max Verstappen's record Formula 1 winning streak to be Wikipedia material that "nobody reads" was not "the most intelligent thing I could have said".
articles.content:
Verstappen bagged his 10th consecutive grand prix victory last time out at Monza to surpass the nine-race win record jointly held by Red Bull predecessor Sebastian Vettel and Alberto Ascari.
